title: ArtyTorrent Pack 52-Funk Disco House Drum Loops 120-129 bpm-WAV
description:
ArtyTorrent Pack 52-Funk Disco House Drum Loops 120-129 bpm-WAV
---------------------------------------------------------------

We&#039;ve reached the classic house tempo of 120bpm at last! I love funky loops. This pack contains some really nice disco-style loops for your funky house productions running from 120-129 bpm. These loops are also great for chopping up and timestretching.

Torrent contains 6 RAR files with 187 loops
-------------------------------------------
Loopmasters Disco House 120 (31 loops)
Loopmasters Disco House 125 (62 loops)
Loopmasters Disco House 128 (52 loops)
Misc Funk Disco 120-129 (14 loops)
Street Beats 120-129 (5 loops)
Ueb Disco Deluxe 120-125 (23 loops)


All samples have been normalized and acidized and are 16-bit WAVs at 44.1KHz, looped precisely and containing the approx bpm in the filenames.

The samples are from a variety of sources including CDs produced by Loopmasters, Sonic Foundry/Sony, and Ueberschall.

--
Arty - "Funky funky"
13th February 2008.
